Vital Point to Capture?(35)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par If this shape appears in the actual game, it is easy to let Black live.
\par However if White makes use of the shortage of liberties it is simple to capture Black.
\par
\par The first move decides everything.
\par
\par }
