Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's severe attack with cut at 1 is \cf1\b aiming at the shortage of liberties\cf0\b0 .
\par Black has to play at 2 and then breaking the eye with White 3 is a brilliant move. Black can't cut at A, can he?
\par
\par So Black is dead.
\par
\par
\par }
