Dia. 02 White 2, Good Move
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Against White \'a1\'e2 if Black 1 could work, it would be nice, but \cf1\b White 2 \cf0\b0 is a \cf1\b good move\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par This time there is a shortage of liberties on the right side, so Black can't play at A.
\par
\par
\par }
