Dia. 03 Wrong Order
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par First White wedge-in at 1 is \cf1\b wrong order\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par After Black 2, White plays double dansu but Black lives with 4 and 6.
\par
\par White captured the three Black stones but globally it is not satisfying.
\par This problem shows how important is the order of the moves.
\par
\par
\par }
