Dia. 04 The Opponent's Vital Point
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Attacking with White 1 is meaningless.
\par After Black connects with 2, White can't capture Black anymore. 2 was the \cf1\b opponent's vital point\cf0\b0  too.
\par
\par Black lives up to 4.
\par
\par
\par }
